Klopp: &quot;Absolutely deserved win for Bournemouth. We gave the game away. We played static football. It's our fault. It's really bad.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;It's three points lost - no more, these things can happen. You cannot be champions in December, relegated, promoted or whatever.&quot;

Klopp: &quot;If you want to say we are blind, silly, not good enough, then do it. It doesn't influence what I think about my team. That's all.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;Of course we made mistakes today, what else should I say? We missed chances..so we don't have good strikers? We have good strikers.&quot;
